PRIVACY & DATA

Conversation data is transmitted to the selected provider's API (Anthropic,
OpenAI, or Grok) under the user's own API key and is subject to that
provider's terms of service and privacy policy. This tool does not
independently store, log, or transmit conversation content beyond the
active browser session. API keys are session-only and are never written
to persistent storage by this application.

